description: **Critical infrastructure** represents EU-wide high-resolution object-based maps of economic assets and infrastructure systems in coastal flood-prone areas. -**Spatial coverage**: Coastal LAU (municipality level) -**Sources**: Satellite imagery and opensource databases (OpenStreetMap among others) -**Common usage**: Supports building exposure assessments, informs coastal resilience and adaptation planning, engages stakeholders with accessible data, and helps prioritize investments and strategic land-use decisions. More Info about the dataset: User Handbook
